snippet.title: Wholesome Cats - Android/iOS Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Play on iOS (https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/wholesome-cats/id1436937938), Android (https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.AngelaHe.WholesomeCats), or web (https://zephyo.itch.io/wholesome-cats)!

(＾・ω・＾) ﾉ Befriend and collect cute, nice cats as you explore an island of wholesome kitties! ♡

Wholesome Cats Github: https://github.com/zephyo/Wholesome-Cats 
Facebook: https://facebook.com/zephybite 
Tumblr: http://zephyo.tumblr.com 
Twitter: https://twitter.com/zephybite 

Music credit to Cityfires (https://soundcloud.com/cityfires).
